  Advanced Face Compositing

Sure, you can use D-ID to animate a face. But what if you want more life from your character's performance? That's where this video comes into play. In this video, I'm going to show you how to use a unique tool called MyHeritage to add facial movements to your videos. The workflow can be tricky to grasp, but once you do it a few times you'll have no trouble creating beautiful animated characters.
